    class HRegion.RegionScannerImpl
extends Object
implements RegionScanner, Shipper, RpcCallback
    RegionScannerImpl is used to combine scanners from multiple Stores (aka column families).

      • nextRaw

        public boolean nextRaw(List<Cell> outResults)
                throws IOException
        从接口复制的说明: RegionScanner
        Grab the next row's worth of values. This is a special internal method to be called from coprocessor hooks to avoid expensive setup. Caller must set the thread's readpoint, start and close a region operation, an synchronize on the scanner object. Caller should maintain and update metrics. See RegionScanner.nextRaw(List, ScannerContext)
        指定者:
        nextRaw 在接口中 RegionScanner
        参数:
        outResults - return output array
        返回:
        true if more rows exist after this one, false if scanner is done
        抛出:
        IOException - e

      • nextRaw

        public boolean nextRaw(List<Cell> outResults,
                       ScannerContext scannerContext)
                throws IOException
        从接口复制的说明: RegionScanner
        Grab the next row's worth of values. The ScannerContext is used to enforce and track any limits associated with this call. Any progress that exists in the ScannerContext prior to calling this method will be LOST if ScannerContext.getKeepProgress() is false. Upon returning from this method, the ScannerContext will contain information about the progress made towards the limits. This is a special internal method to be called from coprocessor hooks to avoid expensive setup. Caller must set the thread's readpoint, start and close a region operation, an synchronize on the scanner object. Example: HRegion region = ...; RegionScanner scanner = ... MultiVersionConcurrencyControl.setThreadReadPoint(scanner.getMvccReadPoint()); region.startRegionOperation(); try { synchronized(scanner) { ... boolean moreRows = scanner.nextRaw(values); ... } } finally { region.closeRegionOperation(); }
        指定者:
        nextRaw 在接口中 RegionScanner
        参数:
        outResults - return output array
        scannerContext - The ScannerContext instance encapsulating all limits that should be tracked during calls to this method. The progress towards these limits can be tracked within this instance.
        返回:
        true if more rows exist after this one, false if scanner is done
        抛出:
        IOException - e

      • moreCellsInRow

        private boolean moreCellsInRow(Cell nextKv,
                               Cell currentRowCell)
        Based on the nextKv in the heap, and the current row, decide whether or not there are more cells to be read in the heap. If the row of the nextKv in the heap matches the current row then there are more cells to be read in the row.
        参数:
        nextKv -
        currentRowCell -
        返回:
        true When there are more cells in the row to be read

      • filterRow

        private boolean filterRow()
                   throws IOException
        This function is to maintain backward compatibility for 0.94 filters. HBASE-6429 combines both filterRow & filterRow(List<KeyValue> kvs) functions. While 0.94 code or older, it may not implement hasFilterRow as HBase-6429 expects because 0.94 hasFilterRow() only returns true when filterRow(List<KeyValue> kvs) is overridden not the filterRow(). Therefore, the filterRow() will be skipped.
        抛出:
        IOException
